Package musicplaylist

Class MusicLibrary

java.lang.Object
musicplaylist.MusicLibrary
public class MusicLibrary extends Object
Represents a music library that holds various types of media. This class manages a collection of musicplaylist.MusicMedia objects, providing methods to add media, display the library content, and play sections of media based on the title.
Version:
1.0
Author:
Emma Lee, Sam Ordonez, Vandy Saxena, Chris Helmhold
